35:15.083 --> 35:18.542
OH, MY GOD. POOR NIC.

35:18.625 --> 35:21.542
AND SHE WAS SAYING SHE SHOULD
HAVE DONE IT A LONG TIME AGO

35:21.625 --> 35:25.250
WHEN SHE KNEW WHAT SHE WANTED,
BUT SHE WAS TOO SCARED.

35:25.333 --> 35:26.542
BRIAN...

35:26.625 --> 35:31.750
LISTEN, I-I SPENT THE LAST
FIVE HOURS IN MY CRAPPY CAR.

35:31.834 --> 35:34.250
I GOT TWO SPEEDING TICKETS.

35:34.333 --> 35:38.083
BECAUSE I WANTED TO TELL YOU THAT...

35:42.458 --> 35:44.875
