35:48.041 --> 35:50.125
LONG BEFORE WE KISSED LAST NIGHT.

35:55.625 --> 35:59.125
BUT NOW THAT I'M HERE,
I REALIZE I CAN'T SAY THAT,

35:59.250 --> 36:02.709
BECAUSE IT DOESN'T MATTER
HOW I FEEL ABOUT YOU. I...

36:02.792 --> 36:05.959
I CAN'T DO THAT TO ADAM OR YOU.

36:08.625 --> 36:11.709
BECAUSE IF I'M GONNA BE
THE BEST MAN IN YOUR WEDDING,

36:11.834 --> 36:14.125
THEN, UM...

36:14.208 --> 36:17.625
I'D BETTER ACTUALLY BE THE BEST MAN.

36:19.250 --> 36:22.333
HEY, BABY, I WAS JUST, UH, WAITING OVER...

36:22.417 --> 36:23.750
BRIAN.

36:23.834 --> 36:25.208
OH, MY GOD.

36:25.333 --> 36:27.125
UH, WHEN DID YOU GET HERE?

36:27.208 --> 36:30.542
I JUST FLEW IN A COUPLE
OF HOURS AGO FROM NEW YORK

36:30.667 --> 36:33.500
TO HOOK UP WITH MY GIRL. YOU GUYS, UH,
GONNA GET MARRIED?

36:33.625 --> 36:36.667
