38:05.542 --> 38:07.083
HELLO.

38:07.208 --> 38:09.083
WHAT ABOUT JACK? GOOD MORNING, MOMMY.

38:09.208 --> 38:10.709
GOOD MORNING, MOMMY.

38:10.792 --> 38:14.250
GOOD MORNING. GOOD MORNING.

38:14.333 --> 38:16.458
